Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,SANSHU MIDDLE SCHOOL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,PREPARATION ROOM\NHERO CLUB'S CLUB ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.35,0:00:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sanshu Middle School's Hero Club\Nis a club that does things
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,which would benefit the world\Nwith honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We do our best not to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're likely to succeed if you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We keep things like this in mind\Nand do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hero Club will be\Nmaking our way today as well!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like an essay\Nby a grade-schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's by a middle-school student!\N-I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuna. The town magazine is\Ngoing to introduce
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the Hero Club's activities,\Nso come up with a good slogan, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.63,0:00:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay!\N-Sis,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:01:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we got a lot of thank-you e-mails\Nfrom the kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a great hit the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The parents were\Nlaughing wryly, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.82,0:01:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's not true!\N-Sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you guys started already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.11,0:01:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell asleep during cleaning duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably the only one\Nwho can sleep at a time like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.29,0:01:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I got complimented.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you. Karin-chan doesn't\Ncompliment people that often.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibosshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. We're all here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's start our\NDecember quarter session.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I've laid out all the requests\Nthat have been sent on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of things happened till fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but now Sanshu Middle School's Hero Club\Nis full of energy like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:01:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 1\NSPECTACULAR DAYS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Indian people who came up\Nwith that concept are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, rather than something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,can we do things that'll prepare me\Nfor high-school entrance exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Sonoko-san in\Nsecond year teaching my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Odango!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nogi is smarter\Nthan most home tutors around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know she doesn't seem like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Then I want her\Nto teach me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit worried about you, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't study during the summer\Nbecause there was so much going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your grades were good\Nup till your second year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They were extremely good!\NBut now, they're extremely bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,House!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Too many things happened\Nsince I started third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We can be here now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,because you worked hard,\NFumin-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,PREPARATION ROOM\NHERO CLUB'S CLUB ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Sonoko Nogi, a prospective member\Nof the Hero Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Sonoko Nogi? That Sonoko Nogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a hero over at the Long-Bridge\Ntwo years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to again\Nthank you in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is the legendary hero here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't have anything to do\Nat home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for a reason like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I dropped out of grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How could she say\Nsuch a serious thing so calmly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she was freed from her role,\Nshe asked the amnesty
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to let her go back\Nto having a regular life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I could go back\Nto having a regular life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a weird legendary predecessor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We would love to welcome\Nthe previous great hero, Nogi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just call me Nogi\Nor Sonoko, Fumin-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Fu?\N-Thanks in advance, Nibosshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who told her that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be Ittsun, Itsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Ittsun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuna-chan, I think you'll be Yu-yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, sounds wonderful.\NThen I'll call you Sono-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, that would be great.\N-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is Sancho.\NHe's glad to see you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to see you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's an intriguing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,FIVE ARTICLES OF THE HERO CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how you guys have been\Nenjoying your youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sono-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Hero Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! I'm also going to enjoy my youth\Nfrom now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching\Nfrom my bed the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking that the Hero Club seemed like fun,\Nthat it must be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:05:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I could come back\Nto school again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's study then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start\Nwith my favorite complex matrix.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-I don't understand it at all.\N-A complex number is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming out\Neven though it's a Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,\NI just happened to be free today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NBut you were so cool, Karin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't bad yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hero Club is such a weird club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Something different happens\Nevery day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun will go down,\Nand it'll be tomorrow again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be Monday already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Time goes by so fast on our days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to do homework\Nwhen we get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I already did mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Even though you had\Na game this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it on Saturday.\NThat's to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so good, Karin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's wrong?\N-Oh, no. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A cake! How did you sneak that in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I had my home economics class today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-Did you make that, Itsuki-chan?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought it\Nbecause I made too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well, my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What a unique taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You should say that\Nshe's expressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-Setting aside what it looks like...\N-It tastes good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady, you're a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Itsuki finally made something edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, that's actually more hurtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ittsun, Ittsun, let's open a shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make it a franchise\Nin the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonoko-san, your dreams are so big\Nthat I can't tell if it's a joke or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But I appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can keep on eating this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead then, Karin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Itsuki should have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I already had some during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonoko-san, please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who should have it,\Nclub president.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ate two of them, I'd have to be\Nconcerned about my femininity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fu, why did you cut it\Ninto five pieces in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. It was from habit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A habit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well\Nit was for no special reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cut into five pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I just used math.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Botamochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking maybe we ate\Nbotamochi in the club room before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you made it\Nin home economics class before right, Yuna-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Snack time is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's practice for Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,YUKI YUNA IS A HERO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,OFF-LIMITS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally was able to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see. How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess\Nthat wasn't the right question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,GIN MINOWA
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of not seeing\Nfor a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the shop in Ines that had\Nthe Shoyu-mame flavor was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The flow of time is always cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Mino-san.\NI joined the Hero Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The one\Nin Sanshu Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're neck and neck\Nwith our team.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is a Saturday,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but all of us are going to put on\Na play at a kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do\Nan excellent job as a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I made this at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered\Nhow you used to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and made it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you, Mino-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to compliment it\Nif it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one is for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san, why do you think\NI made three of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,MONUMENT TO THE WAR DEAD
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nogi isn't here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't read the messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonoko-san was\Nso excited about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she's only a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll have to do this\Nwithout the tree today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong, Yuna?\NIt's time for our performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of feel restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys feel like that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuna-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we cancel today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in the Hero Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for doing this today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The kids have been\Nlooking forward to today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been waiting anxiously.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it. Everyone is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the nefarious Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here today to get the kids\Nwho don't listen to their teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's run wild and do as we please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to control yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Satan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give the kids any bad ideas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so stuck-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much\Nthe hero got hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,she never gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because if everyone gave up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,this world would be stuck\Nin the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was bowing down\Nto Satan one after another
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the hero found herself\Nall alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No one knew the hero was all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I become all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A hero is still...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Still,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,a hero is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because as long as\Nwe don't give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,there will still be hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I lose everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose my\Nmost important friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's wrong?\N-She's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuna-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:15:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised that\NI'll always be with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuna-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,PREPARATION ROOM\NHERO CLUB'S CLUB ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Listen carefully.\N-Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The memory we have now isn't real.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Something horrible is happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't know what that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but we're pretending that\Nit didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, Yuna--\N-I
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,remember now. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hero Club had\Nanother really important friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we could forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we should have forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuna, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, try to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Togo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There used to be a girl called\NMimori Togo here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come to think of it,\Nwhere is Togo now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Togo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimori Togo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sonoko from the Nogi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're that Sonoko Nogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same class from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:16:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Wasshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-My surprise was a big success!\N-Sonocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Wasshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,PREPARATION ROOM\NHERO CLUB'S CLUB ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Sonoko Nogi,\Na prospective member of the Hero Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonoko Nogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a hero over\Nat the Long-Bridge two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to again thank you in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I could study\Nwith you again, Sonocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Scold me if I fall asleep\Nduring class, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be careful\Nnot to fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if Togo is her mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The circle of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sounds cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It means a fateful encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the girl of fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-Fortune!\N-Wealth and happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It also means\Nan unavoidable situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the serious face,\NItsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,National Defense Mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The mysterious hero\Nwho's a sensation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-There's someone like that?\N-Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,People are calling us\Nto protect their country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They're screaming\Nfor us to protect love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A patriotic warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,National Defense Mask is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,People are calling us\Nto protect their country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're screaming\Nfor us to protect love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A patriotic warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,National Defense Mask is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-I got you!\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the National Defense Mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show up as much as I can\Nwhen people are being exposed to evil threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you, Togo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know where to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The National Defense Mask is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuna-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving me\Nthe other day
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-Would you shake my hand?\N-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She lost her wallet at night
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and the National Defense Mask\Nlooked for it with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I'm really comfortable\Ntalking to you, National Defense Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how come you're here\Nat the Hero Club today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuna-chan, I'm the National Defense Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea that Togo-san was\Nthe National Defense Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're serious, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you mean you're sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I recovered,\NI've been in agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that\NI destroyed part of the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it was\Nan impulse of the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a fact that I put the world\Nin danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know how I could make amends for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought about ways to atone\Nfor my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you came up\Nwith the National Defense Mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasshi, you're really extreme now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel,\Nbut you're rushing it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The National Defense Mask is\Nso cool! I want to become one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,despite my appearance, I'm\Nthe second National Defense Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be the third one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't create more of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,if people like Karin mimic you\Nand become the Dried Sardine Mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't mimic them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Togo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We feel the same way about wanting\Nto do your best for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right, Wasshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can rely on us\Nif there's something going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuna-chan, Sonocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Togo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't any of us have\Nany memory of Togo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if she never existed\Nin this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm the club president,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,yet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:22:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,where are you,\Nand what are you doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:23:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,ON THE NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.48,0:24:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.89,0:24:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go there without stopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.60,0:24:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just plain dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.11,0:24:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cool ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.27,0:24:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-Make sure to come back, Yuna.\N-Togo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.73,0:24:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save her\Nover and over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.36,0:24:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 2\NIMPORTANT MEMORIES
